	<body>
		<outline text="/scripting.com/code/instantoutlinesrepo/">
			<outline text="readme.md" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 12:55:20 GMT">
				<outline text="# instantOutlines" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 12:55:34 GMT">
					<outline text="Sharing outlines between apps using GitHub as the intermediary." created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 12:55:54 GMT"/>
					</outline>
				<outline text="### Demo app" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:08:45 GMT">
					<outline text="Here's a &lt;a href=&quot;http://scripting.com/code/instantoutlinesrepo/demo/&quot;&gt;demo app&lt;/a&gt; that watches an outline that flows through this repo. " created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:08:50 GMT"/>
					<outline text="It's an outline that's generated from threads I post &lt;a href=&quot;https://twitter.com/davewiner&quot;&gt;on Twitter&lt;/a&gt;. " created="Sat, 12 Jun 2021 15:23:11 GMT"/>
					<outline text="You don't have to reload it to see my updates, they will appear automatically." created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:09:41 GMT"/>
					<outline text="The source code is &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/scripting/instantOutlines/tree/main/demo&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;. " created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:09:56 GMT"/>
					</outline>
				<outline text="### If you're a developer..." created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:28:53 GMT">
					<outline text="You can subscribe to any of these outlines. Just follow the example of the demo app." created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:29:01 GMT">
						<outline text="0. Start by subscribing to &lt;a href=&quot;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/scripting/instantOutlines/main/outlines/twitter/davewiner.opml&quot;&gt;my outline&lt;/a&gt;. I generally update about 20 times a day, pretty reliably. " created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 14:02:28 GMT"/>
						<outline text="1. You'll read the outline initially. " created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:30:11 GMT"/>
						<outline text="1. You'll set up a web socket handler to subscribe to the outline. " created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:29:19 GMT"/>
						<outline text="2. Wait for an updated outline to come over the wire. " created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:30:01 GMT"/>
						</outline>
					<outline text="All of these are illustrated in the demo app. " created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 14:03:40 GMT"/>
					<outline text="When you have a demo running, let us know by tweet, email or a post in the Issues section here. " created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 14:04:33 GMT"/>
					</outline>
				<outline text="### This is a working site" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:00:20 GMT">
					<outline text="1. Outlines flow into the site. The outlines contain tweets of users we're following." created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:00:36 GMT"/>
					<outline text="2. I have an app running on my desktop that checks several Twitter accounts once a minute. When one of these users tweets, we add it to a calendar-structured outline, and using the GitHub API, post it here. in the outlines folder. " created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:05:38 GMT"/>
					<outline text="3. I've set up a GitHub web mook, that notifies a server app that the outline has updated. " created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:06:24 GMT"/>
					<outline text="4. We then send a message, via web sockets, to any app that's subscribed to the outline, with the full OPML text of the outline. It's totally up to the individual apps what they do with the outline." created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:06:57 GMT"/>
					<outline text="5. The net effect is that the changed outlines flow to any app that wants to subscribe to them." created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:03:35 GMT"/>
					</outline>
				<outline text="### socketServer" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:10:09 GMT">
					<outline text="The source for the server is here." created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:10:14 GMT"/>
					</outline>
				<outline text="### Philosophy" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:13:30 GMT">
					<outline text="You can run your own server if you want, flowing outlines from your GitHub repo. " created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:12:10 GMT"/>
					<outline text="There's nothing exclusive about anything here. " created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:12:32 GMT"/>
					<outline text="I don't really have an interest in being the central node, I just want to set up a prototype, work with other developers to interop, build apps off the power of instant outlining. " created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:12:43 GMT"/>
					</outline>
				<outline text="### OPML everywhere" created="Sat, 12 Jun 2021 15:25:24 GMT">
					<outline text="A couple of things about OPML." created="Sat, 12 Jun 2021 15:25:32 GMT">
						<outline text="1. I used an outliner to write this site and the example app. The source is &lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/scripting/instantOutlines/blob/main/misc/source.opml&quot;&gt;here&lt;/a&gt;." created="Sat, 12 Jun 2021 15:25:38 GMT"/>
						<outline text="2. A &lt;a href=&quot;http://this.how/opmlChecklist/&quot;&gt;checklist&lt;/a&gt; of basic info for devs using OPML for interop." created="Sat, 12 Jun 2021 15:25:53 GMT"/>
						</outline>
					</outline>
				<outline text="### License" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:02:28 GMT">
					<outline text="The writing on this site is copyrighted. " created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:02:32 GMT"/>
					<outline text="The code we're demonstrating is MIT-licensed. " created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:02:48 GMT"/>
					</outline>
				<outline text="### Updates" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:13:55 GMT">
					<outline text="#### 6/11/21 by DW" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:14:00 GMT">
						<outline text="When there are updates they will appear here. " created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:14:07 GMT"/>
						</outline>
					</outline>
				<outline text="### Discussion" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:14:21 GMT">
					<outline text="Please use the &lt;a href=&quot;/issues&quot;&gt;issues section&lt;/a&gt; of this repo. Be friendly and let's have fun. :-)" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 13:14:27 GMT"/>
					</outline>
				</outline>
			<outline text="demo/code.js">
				<outline text="const urlOpmlFile = &quot;https://raw.githubusercontent.com/scripting/instantOutlines/master/outlines/twitter/davewiner.opml&quot;;" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 12:28:22 GMT"/>
				<outline text="var urlSocketServer;" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 12:43:51 GMT"/>
				<outline text="var mySocket = undefined; " created="Mon, 12 Apr 2021 16:16:47 GMT"/>
				<outline text="" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 14:07:24 GMT"/>
				<outline text="var opmltextLog = new Array ();" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 14:07:24 GMT"/>
				<outline text="" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 11:58:08 GMT"/>
				<outline text="function getObjectFromOpmltext (opmltext) {" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 11:58:09 GMT">
					<outline text="var xstruct = xmlCompile (opmltext);"/>
					<outline text="var adrhead = xmlGetAddress (xstruct, &quot;head&quot;);" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 21:07:11 GMT"/>
					<outline text="var adrbody = xmlGetAddress (xstruct, &quot;body&quot;);" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 11:59:08 GMT"/>
					<outline text="var theObject = {" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 11:59:08 GMT">
						<outline text="opml: {" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 11:59:16 GMT">
							<outline text="head: xmlGetSubValues (adrhead)," created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 11:59:20 GMT"/>
							<outline text="body: outlineToJson (adrbody)" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 11:59:37 GMT"/>
							<outline text="}" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 12:00:39 GMT"/>
							</outline>
						<outline text="}" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 12:00:40 GMT"/>
						</outline>
					<outline text="return (theObject);" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 11:59:08 GMT"/>
					<outline text="}" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 11:58:19 GMT"/>
					</outline>
				<outline text="function viewTheOutline (opmltext) {" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 16:51:40 GMT">
					<outline text="var theOutline = getObjectFromOpmltext (opmltext);" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 12:02:08 GMT"/>
					<outline text="" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 12:07:14 GMT"/>
					<outline text="var htmltext = &quot;&quot;, indentlevel = 0;" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 18:52:52 GMT"/>
					<outline text="function add (s) {" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 18:53:04 GMT">
						<outline text="htmltext += filledString (&quot;\t&quot;, indentlevel) + s + &quot;\n&quot;;" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 18:57:55 GMT"/>
						<outline text="}" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 18:57:50 GMT"/>
						</outline>
					<outline text="" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 12:03:41 GMT"/>
					<outline text="//add a table of the head elements in the OPML" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 12:03:23 GMT">
						<outline text="add (&quot;&lt;table&gt;&quot;); indentlevel++;" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 21:16:19 GMT"/>
						<outline text="for (var x in theOutline.opml.head) {" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 21:15:10 GMT">
							<outline text="add (&quot;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td class=\&quot;tdRight\&quot;&gt;&quot; + x + &quot;: &lt;/td&gt;&lt;td&gt;&quot; + theOutline.opml.head [x] + &quot;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&quot;);" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 21:15:24 GMT"/>
							<outline text="}" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 21:15:19 GMT"/>
							</outline>
						<outline text="add (&quot;&lt;/table&gt;&quot;); indentlevel--;" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 21:16:19 GMT"/>
						<outline text="$(&quot;#idHeadElementsViewer&quot;).html (htmltext);" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 16:58:17 GMT"/>
						</outline>
					<outline text="//add an indented outline of the body from the OPML" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 12:06:43 GMT">
						<outline text="htmltext = &quot;&quot;; indentlevel = 0;" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 18:52:52 GMT"/>
						<outline text="function addSubsHtml (node) {" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 18:52:07 GMT">
							<outline text="add (&quot;&lt;ul&gt;&quot;); indentlevel++;" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 18:54:17 GMT"/>
							<outline text="node.subs.forEach (function (sub) {" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 18:54:17 GMT">
								<outline text="add (&quot;&lt;li&gt;&quot; + sub.text + &quot;&lt;/li&gt;&quot;);" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 18:54:46 GMT"/>
								<outline text="if (sub.subs !== undefined) {" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 18:55:12 GMT">
									<outline text="addSubsHtml (sub);" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 18:55:37 GMT"/>
									<outline text="}" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 18:55:21 GMT"/>
									</outline>
								<outline text="});" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 18:54:26 GMT"/>
								</outline>
							<outline text="add (&quot;&lt;/ul&gt;&quot;); indentlevel--;" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 18:54:17 GMT"/>
							<outline text="}" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 18:52:23 GMT"/>
							</outline>
						<outline text="addSubsHtml (theOutline.opml.body);"/>
						<outline text="$(&quot;#idOutlineViewer&quot;).html (htmltext);" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 16:58:17 GMT"/>
						</outline>
					<outline text="" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 12:07:07 GMT"/>
					<outline text="}" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 16:51:51 GMT"/>
					</outline>
				<outline text="function wsWatchForChange (urlSocketServer) {">
					<outline text="if (mySocket === undefined) {">
						<outline text="mySocket = new WebSocket (urlSocketServer); "/>
						<outline text="mySocket.onopen = function (evt) {">
							<outline text="var msg = &quot;watch &quot; + urlOpmlFile;"/>
							<outline text="mySocket.send (msg);"/>
							<outline text="console.log (&quot;wsWatchForChange: socket is open. sent msg == &quot; + msg);" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 12:56:13 GMT"/>
							<outline text="};"/>
							</outline>
						<outline text="mySocket.onmessage = function (evt) {">
							<outline text="var s = evt.data;"/>
							<outline text="if (s !== undefined) { //no error">
								<outline text="const updatekey = &quot;update\r&quot;;"/>
								<outline text="if (beginsWith (s, updatekey)) { //it's an update">
									<outline text="var opmltext = stringDelete (s, 1, updatekey.length);"/>
									<outline text="console.log (&quot;wsWatchForChange: update received along with &quot; + opmltext.length + &quot; chars of OPML text.&quot;);" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 12:56:13 GMT"/>
									<outline text="viewTheOutline (opmltext);" created="Wed, 16 Jan 2013 00:08:18 GMT" pgfnum="17213"/>
									<outline text="opmltextLog.push (opmltext);" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 14:08:15 GMT"/>
									<outline text="}"/>
									</outline>
								<outline text="}"/>
								</outline>
							<outline text="};"/>
							</outline>
						<outline text="mySocket.onclose = function (evt) {">
							<outline text="mySocket = undefined;"/>
							<outline text="};"/>
							</outline>
						<outline text="mySocket.onerror = function (evt) {">
							<outline text="console.log (&quot;wsWatchForChange: socket for outline &quot; + urlOpmlFile + &quot; received an error.&quot;);" created="Wed, 31 Mar 2021 14:26:24 GMT"/>
							<outline text="};"/>
							</outline>
						<outline text="}"/>
						</outline>
					<outline text="}"/>
					</outline>
				<outline text="function everySecond () {" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 12:31:51 GMT">
					<outline text="wsWatchForChange (urlSocketServer); " created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 12:31:55 GMT"/>
					<outline text="}" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 12:31:54 GMT"/>
					</outline>
				<outline text="function startup () {">
					<outline text="console.log (&quot;startup&quot;);"/>
					<outline text="opTypeIcons.tweet = undefined; //6/10/21 by DW"/>
					<outline text="$(&quot;#idOpmlLink&quot;).attr (&quot;href&quot;, urlOpmlFile);" created="Fri, 11 Jun 2021 12:27:43 GMT"/>
					<outline text="readHttpFile (urlOpmlFile, function (opmltext) {">
						<outline text="if (opmltext === undefined) {" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 12:38:15 GMT">
							<outline text="alertDialog (&quot;There was an error reading the OPML file.&quot;);" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 12:38:34 GMT"/>
							<outline text="}" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 12:38:28 GMT"/>
							</outline>
						<outline text="else {" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 12:38:54 GMT">
							<outline text="var xstruct = xmlCompile (opmltext);"/>
							<outline text="var adropml = xmlGetAddress (xstruct, &quot;opml&quot;);" created="Wed, 30 Oct 2013 17:54:25 GMT" pgfnum="30678"/>
							<outline text="var adrhead = xmlGetAddress (adropml, &quot;head&quot;);" created="Wed, 30 Oct 2013 17:54:25 GMT" pgfnum="30678"/>
							<outline text="urlSocketServer = xmlGetValue (adrhead, &quot;urlUpdateSocket&quot;); //set global"/>
							<outline text="wsWatchForChange (urlSocketServer);"/>
							<outline text="viewTheOutline (opmltext);" created="Wed, 16 Jan 2013 00:08:18 GMT" pgfnum="17213"/>
							<outline text="opmltextLog.push (opmltext);" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 14:08:15 GMT"/>
							<outline text="self.setInterval (everySecond, 1000); //start the websocket "/>
							<outline text="}" created="Thu, 10 Jun 2021 12:38:58 GMT"/>
							</outline>
						<outline text="});"/>
						</outline>
					<outline text="}"/>
					</outline>
				</outline>
			<outline text="demo/index.html">
				<outline text="&lt;html&gt;">
					<outline text="&lt;head&gt;">
						<outline text="&lt;title&gt;Socket Client&lt;/title&gt;"/>
